.TH "tsi721_cread_dma" 9 "tsi721_cread_dma" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
tsi721_cread_dma \- Generate a RapidIO maintenance read transaction using Tsi721 BDMA engine.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" tsi721_cread_dma
.BI "(struct rio_mport *mport "  ","
.BI "int index "  ","
.BI "u16 destid "  ","
.BI "u8 hopcount "  ","
.BI "u32 offset "  ","
.BI "int len "  ","
.BI "u32 *data "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mport" 12
RapidIO master port control structure
.IP "index" 12
ID of RapdiIO interface
.IP "destid" 12
Destination ID of transaction
.IP "hopcount" 12
Number of hops to target device
.IP "offset" 12
Offset into configuration space
.IP "len" 12
Length (in bytes) of the maintenance transaction
.IP "data" 12
-- undescribed --
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Generates a RapidIO maintenance read transaction.
Returns 0 on success and -EINVAL or -EFAULT on failure.
